# /manifest.webmanifest was generated by vite-plugin-pwa before the PWA layer was
# retired (vite.config.js: `manifest: false`). Nothing links to it any more, but a
# stale copy is still sitting in Cloudflare's edge cache. This 301 makes the path
# resolve to the site's real hand-authored manifest instead of a 404 or a stale
# body, for as long as anything out there still asks for it.
/manifest.webmanifest  /site.webmanifest  301
